### encrypting existing files ###
ansible-vault encrypt --help

given a file already exists:
whatever.yml

encrypt with prompt for passsword:
ansible-vault encrypt whatever.yml

encrypt using a password script:
ansible-vault encrypt --vault-password-file password.sh whatever.yml

# encrypte multipke files
ansible-vault encrypt whatever.yml another_file.yml third_file.yml

#notes
create cannot encrypt multiple files
if you try to encrypt an encrpyted file you will get an error.
